---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Legal Notice — Eddie Miller Agency"
  description="Legal notice for the Eddie Miller Agency website. Publisher, hosting, intellectual property, personal data and cookies."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-40 md:pb-24 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 bg-cream">
    <article class="max-w-container mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-16">
      <div class="max-w-[65ch]">
        <div class="bg-sand/40 border border-sand rounded-lg px-5 py-4 mb-10 md:mb-14">
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-sans text-stone">
            This is an English translation. The legally binding version is available in French at <a href="/mentions-legales" class="text-terracotta transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-terracotta-dark">/mentions-legales</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-[2rem] md:text-[3rem] font-serif font-normal leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal mb-10 md:mb-14">
          Legal Notice
        </h1>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Website Publisher
          </h2>
          <div class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone space-y-1">
            <p>Eddie Miller Agency</p>
            <p>Sole proprietorship (Auto-entrepreneur)</p>
            <p>SIRET: 877 928 176 00024</p>
            <p>41 Rue du Montparnasse, 75014 Paris, France</p>
            <p>VAT not applicable — article 293 B of the French General Tax Code (CGI)</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:contact@eddiemiller.agency" class="text-terracotta transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-terracotta-dark">contact@eddiemiller.agency</a></p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Hosting
          </h2>
          <div class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone space-y-1">
            <p>Vercel Inc.</p>
            <p>340 S Lemon Ave #4133</p>
            <p>Walnut, CA 91789, United States</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Intellectual Property
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            All content on this website (text, graphics, structure) is the exclusive property of Eddie Miller Agency. Any reproduction is prohibited without prior authorization.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Personal Data and GDPR
          </h2>
          <div class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone space-y-4">
            <p><strong class="text-charcoal">Data controller:</strong> Eddie Miller Agency, 75014 Paris, France.</p>
            <p><strong class="text-charcoal">Data collected:</strong> business name, business type, location, email address, phone number (optional). As part of our services: professional contact details, Google Business profile information, online presence data.</p>
            <p><strong class="text-charcoal">Purpose:</strong> responding to your free diagnostic request, delivering the ordered services, issuing invoices and managing the business relationship.</p>
            <p><strong class="text-charcoal">Legal basis:</strong> performance of a contract (Article 6.1.b of the GDPR).</p>
            <p><strong class="text-charcoal">Retention period:</strong> duration of the contractual relationship + 3 years. Invoices: 10 years (accounting obligation).</p>
            <p><strong class="text-charcoal">Recipients:</strong> data is processed solely by Eddie Miller Agency. It is not shared with any third party, except for technical subcontractors (Vercel for hosting, Stripe for payment).</p>
            <p><strong class="text-charcoal">Your rights:</strong> in accordance with the GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, delete, object to, and port your data. To exercise these rights: <a href="mailto:contact@eddiemiller.agency" class="text-terracotta transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-terracotta-dark">contact@eddiemiller.agency</a>. Response time: 30 days maximum.</p>
            <p><strong class="text-charcoal">Complaints:</strong> in the event of a dispute, you may file a complaint with the CNIL (<a href="https://www.cnil.fr" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-terracotta transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-terracotta-dark">www.cnil.fr</a>), the French data protection authority.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Cookies
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            This website uses Plausible Analytics, a privacy-friendly analytics tool that does not set any cookies and does not collect any personal data.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
